All Classes

  • Class Description
    AppInfo
    Gathers information about the current and latest version of the manager.
    ArduinoPin
    Represents an Arduino pin, with an id (its number on the Arduino board), a name and a value.
    ConnectionException
    Exception related to connections, sockets, communication and data transfer in general.
    ConnectionException.Type
    Enum representing the kind of error detected.
    ControlPanel
    The control panel.
    ControlPanel.AbstractPinDialog
    Abstract JDialog to ask the user for a pin, its name and its value.
    ControlPanel.UserInfoProvider
    User info provider.
    DigitalPinDialog
    JDialog to ask the user for a digital pin, its name and its value.
    INDIArduinoDriver
    INDI Arduino pin driver.
    INDIServer
    A simple INDI Server that basically sends all messages from drivers and clients and vice versa, just performing basic checks of messages integrity.
    Main
    The main class of the application.
    Main.ExitCodes
    A list of common exit codes.
    Main.OperatingSystem
    Enum that lists all the possible operating systems.
    PinArray
    Represents a list of Arduino pins.
    PinValue
    Represents the value of an Arduino pin.
    PinValue.ValueType
    All the possible value types for Arduino pins.
    PwmPinDialog
    JDialog to ask the user for a PWM pin, its name and its value.
    ScpUploader
    Upload file to SSH server.
    SerialMessageListener
    Serial message listener interface.
    SerialPortImpl
    Abstract manager for serial ports with listeners.
    SerialPortMultiplexer
    Serial port multiplexer/duplicator.
    ServerMiniWindow
    Mini window shown in server mode to stop the application (if GUI is enabled).
    Settings
    Stores all the app's settings.
    UnixSerialPortMultiplexer
    Serial port multiplexer/duplicator for Linux/Unix that uses socat (via UnixSerialPortMultiplexer.SocatRunner).
    Updater
    AVR Hex firmware uploader/updater utility.
    Updater.AvrdudeListener
    Avrdude listener.
    WindowsSerialPortMultiplexer
    Serial port multiplexer/duplicator for Windows, using JNI.
